function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
$cont = @file_get_contents('changelog.json.php');
if ($cont === false) err('Cannot read changelog.json.php');
$json = @json_decode($cont, true);
if ($json === null) err('Cannot parse changelog.json.php');
$latest_version = false;
foreach ($json as $v) {
	if (isset($v['version']) && (substr($v['version'], -4) != '-dev')) {
		$latest_version = $v['version'];
		break; // the first item is the latest version
	}
}
if ($latest_version != '2.0.1.23') err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.1.23!');

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.0.0') < 0) {
	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

if (!is_file('TODO')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: TODO');
	writefile_105();
	if (!is_file('TODO')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): TODO');
	} else if (sha1_file('TODO') != '5d74d5325ef7856a8359666d7c14624e52d7eee2') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): TODO');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('TODO', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of TODO');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '5d74d5325ef7856a8359666d7c14624e52d7eee2') {
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '61a0b9aea0212721df9a58b021fc90bcf8d271ed') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: TODO');
			$tmp = pathinfo('TODO');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('TODO')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('TODO', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_105();
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '5d74d5325ef7856a8359666d7c14624e52d7eee2') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): TODO');
		}
	}
}

	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('YW5pZWwgTWFyc2NoYWxsIChWaWFUaGlua1NvZnQpIiwKCQkiY2hhbmdlcyI6IFsKCQkJIkluaXRpYWwgV29yay1Jbi1Qcm9ncmVzcyBTVk4gcmVsZWFzZSIKCQldCgl9LAoJewoJCSJ2ZXJzaW9uIjogIjIuMC4wLjEiLAoJCSJkYXRlIjogIjIwMTktMDMtMTIgMjM6'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('MDc6NTAgKzAxMDAiLAoJCSJhdXRob3IiOiAiRGFuaWVsIE1hcnNjaGFsbCAoVmlhVGhpbmtTb2Z0KSIsCgkJImNoYW5nZXMiOiBbCgkJCSJDcmVhdGVkIFNWTiByb290IGRpcmVjdG9yaWVzIgoJCV0KCX0KXQo='));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: changelog.json.php');
	writefile_106();
	if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): changelog.json.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('changelog.json.php') != 'ac2acdaf194731dbfeec52017203aae97d25373b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('changelog.json.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of changelog.json.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== 'ac2acdaf194731dbfeec52017203aae97d25373b') {
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '2127a0b188e13988170fc23a160c6c6b44d57cba') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: changelog.json.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('changelog.json.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('changelog.json.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('changelog.json.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_106();
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== 'ac2acdaf194731dbfeec52017203aae97d25373b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	writefile_107();
	if (!is_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') != '63c2b6db93b4a794a88033db77c220dbdcff1508') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') !== '63c2b6db93b4a794a88033db77c220dbdcff1508') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') !== '6e6ba1989dbd47476c648e8a27cc4cd9076c4a86') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_107();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') !== '63c2b6db93b4a794a88033db77c220dbdcff1508') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/oidplus_custom_guid.md')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/oidplus_custom_guid.md');
	writefile_108();
	if (!is_file('doc/oidplus_custom_guid.md')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/oidplus_custom_guid.md');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/oidplus_custom_guid.md') != '0a534b08ff1adc503ce1bb500b78de692a9dbb99') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/oidplus_custom_guid.md');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/oidplus_custom_guid.md', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/oidplus_custom_guid.md');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/oidplus_custom_guid.md') !== '0a534b08ff1adc503ce1bb500b78de692a9dbb99') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/oidplus_custom_guid.md') !== '19089495fb3e9d57cfd596c26c1b34cbd075a591') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/oidplus_custom_guid.md');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/oidplus_custom_guid.md');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/oidplus_custom_guid.md')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/oidplus_custom_guid.md', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_108();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/oidplus_custom_guid.md') !== '0a534b08ff1adc503ce1bb500b78de692a9dbb99') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/oidplus_custom_guid.md');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	writefile_109();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') != '6720c67a8ba5e4c85766bb916a10919cc8ef16cf') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '6720c67a8ba5e4c85766bb916a10919cc8ef16cf') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '267a63dd81f91b6f427f94068de47eede1396ed3') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_109();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '6720c67a8ba5e4c85766bb916a10919cc8ef16cf') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php') != '03ed3a1e6645cb6dc71ff59a61403d3fad8fc0fa') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php');

		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php') !== '03ed3a1e6645cb6dc71ff59a61403d3fad8fc0fa') {

			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php');

			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_112();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php') !== '03ed3a1e6645cb6dc71ff59a61403d3fad8fc0fa') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php');

			}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	writefile_114();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') != 'edf8fe38d3f9ce01fa1a16a0da0f41bb06c1a99b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== 'edf8fe38d3f9ce01fa1a16a0da0f41bb06c1a99b') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '6102fd5ff54ce299aeac7ff89991491d425cd646') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_114();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== 'edf8fe38d3f9ce01fa1a16a0da0f41bb06c1a99b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
		}
	}
}
